
1. 需要在sms库 建立表如下:

CREATE TABLE `sms_uniq_keys` (
  `id` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `msisdn` varchar(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `uniq_key` varchar(32) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `atime` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `uniq_key` (`uniq_key`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;


需要的php扩展
yaf
mb_string
mysqli

php.ini 中增加yaf配置
[yaf]
yaf.use_namespace=1
yaf.use_spl_autoload=1

需要创建目录
logs=./../logs
logs/sms/oplog
logs/sms/log
logs/sms/bqlog